    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but u said \"when it's manipulated.\" wont that happen with almost any big idea? it feels like u're focusing a lot on the negatives though. can't nationalism also be seen as a positive way to protect a culture from being wiped out by globalism or something? is there a way to have it without all the bad stuff u mentioned?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
